'''双酚A'''（'''Bisphenol A'''，缩写为'''BPA'''），又称'''酚甲烷'''。一种[[化工原料|化工原料]]，是已知的[[内分泌干扰素|内分泌干扰素]]（[[环境荷尔蒙|环境荷尔蒙]]）。它是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，具有两个[[酚|酚]][[官能团|官能团]]。双酚A被用于合成[[聚碳酸酯|聚碳酸酯]]塑料和[[环氧树脂|环氧树脂]]等。

20世纪30年代中期人们就发现了双酚A可以发挥[[雌激素|雌激素]]的作用，它在各个领域应用的争论也就此开始。到2008年，一些政府开始对它在消费领域的安全性提出正式的质疑，并陆续采取措施让相关产品下架。2010年，[[美國食品藥品監督管理局|美國食品藥品監督管理局]]依据在多胎儿、婴儿和幼儿中收集到的数据资料提出进一步的担忧<ref name="U.S. Food and Drug Administration">{{Cite web|url=http://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/PublicHealthFocus/ucm197739.htm|title=Update on Bisphenol A for Use in Food Contact Applications: January 2010|date=2010-01-15|publisher=U.S. Food and Drug Administration|accessdate=2010-01-15|archive-date=2010-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100119070610/http://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/PublicHealthFocus/ucm197739.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>；当年9月，[[加拿大|加拿大]]成为首个将之列为有毒物质的国家<ref>{{Cite journal |url=http://www.gazette.gc.ca/rp-pr/p2/2010/2010-10-13/pdf/g2-14421.pdf |title=Canada Gazette Part II |journal=[[Canada_Gazette|Canada Gazette]] |volume=144 |issue=21 |date=2010-10-13 |pages=1806–18 |access-date=2011-07-07 |archive-date=2012-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318200617/http://www.gazette.gc.ca/rp-pr/p2/2010/2010-10-13/pdf/g2-14421.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/canada-first-to-declare-bisphenol-a-toxic/article1755272/ |title=Canada first to declare bisphenol A toxic |author=Martin Mittelstaedt |work=The Globe and Mail |location=Canada  |date=2010-10-13}}</ref>。在[[欧盟|欧盟]]和加拿大，双酚A被禁止用于生产[[婴儿奶瓶|婴儿奶瓶]]。2012年9月24日，美國[[華盛頓州立大學|華盛頓州立大學]]等機構刊登其研究，公布其在[[獼猴|獼猴]]進行的實驗結果，證實雙酚A會影響獼猴雌性後代的[[生殖系統|生殖系統]]，導致[[卵子|卵子]][[染色體|染色體]]異常<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20120925/144072/1 |title=雙酚A影響雌性生殖系統　獼猴實驗證實 |date=2012-09-25 |accessdate=2012-09-25 |language=zh-hant |publisher=[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]] }}</ref><ref name="Hunt Lawson Gieske Murdoch pp. 17525–17530">{{cite journal | last=Hunt | first=P. A. | last2=Lawson | first2=C. | last3=Gieske | first3=M. | last4=Murdoch | first4=B. | last5=Smith | first5=H. | last6=Marre | first6=A. | last7=Hassold | first7=T. | last8=VandeVoort | first8=C. A. | title=Bisphenol A alters early oogenesis and follicle formation in the fetal ovary of the rhesus monkey | journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences | publisher=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences | volume=109 | issue=43 | date=2012-09-24 | issn=0027-8424 | doi=10.1073/pnas.1207854109 | pages=17525–17530}}</ref>。

==生产==
20世纪80年代，这种化合物在全世界的产量超过了一百万吨<ref name = Fiege/>，而2009年全世界更是出产了超过二百二十万吨双酚A<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE65L6JN20100622?loomia_ow=t0:s0:a49:g43:r3:c0.084942:b35124310:z0|title=Experts demand European action on plastics chemical|publisher=Reuters|date=2010-06-22|accessdate=2011-07-07|archive-date=2019-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190614072154/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-chemical-bpa-health/experts-demand-european-action-on-plastics-chemical-idUSTRE65L6JN20100622?loomia_ow=t0:s0:a49:g43:r3:c0.084942:b35124310:z0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2003年，[[美国|美国]]对双酚A的总消耗为 856,000 吨，其中的 72% 被用于生产[[聚碳酸酯|聚碳酸酯]]塑料， 21% 被用于生产[[环氧树脂|环氧树脂]]<ref name="CERHR"/>。在美国，双酚A应用于与食品接触的领域的比例少于 5% <ref name="epa-action-plan"/>。

双酚A在1891年被俄罗斯化学家{{le|Alexander Dianin}}首次合成<ref name=dianin>{{Cite journal | author=Dianin | title = Zhurnal russkogo fiziko-khimicheskogo obshchestva | volume = 23 | year = 1891 | pages =  492–}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal | first = Theodor | last = Zincke | authorlink = Theodor Zincke | title = Ueber die Einwirkung von Brom und von Chlor auf Phenole: Substitutionsprodukte, Pseudobromide und Pseudochloride | journal=[[Justus_Liebigs_Annalen_der_Chemie|Justus Liebigs Annalen der Chemie]] | year = 1905 | pages = 75–99 | doi = 10.1002/jlac.19053430106 | volume = 343}}</ref>。合成这种[[化合物|化合物]]时，可以采用[[丙酮|丙酮]]与两[[化學當量|当量]]的[[苯酚|苯酚]][[缩合|缩合]]（丙酮的英文单词为 acetone ，首字母为A，也就是“双酚A”名字中“A”的来源）<ref>{{Cite book | last=Uglea | first=Constantin V. | coauthors=Ioan I. Negulescu | title=Synthesis and Characterization of Oligomers | url=https://archive.org/details/synthesischaract0000ugle | year=1991 | publisher=[[CRC_Press|CRC Press]] | page=[https://archive.org/details/synthesischaract0000ugle/page/103 103] | isbn=0849349540}}</ref>。这个反应需要无机强酸，比如[[盐酸|盐酸]]（HCl），或者[[聚苯乙烯磺酸钠|聚苯乙烯磺酸钠]]的[[催化|催化]]。工业生产中，通常会在投料时加入过量的苯酚以保证丙酮被充分反应，而[[异丙苯法|异丙苯法]]得到的粗产品（丙酮与苯酚的混合物）也常被直接用作原料：<ref name=Fiege/>

:[[File:Synthesis_Bisphenol_A.svg|frameless]]

很多种类的[[酮|酮]]也可以发生类似的缩合反应。无论是来自于树脂生产中副产品的[[超真空|超真空]]提纯还是从溶液中提取，商品双酚A需要进一步[[蒸馏|蒸馏]][[提纯|提纯]]。<ref name=Fiege>{{Cite book | first = Helmut | last = Fiege | coauthors = Heinz-Werner Voges, Toshikazu Hamamoto, Sumio Umemura, Tadao Iwata, Hisaya Miki, Yasuhiro Fujita, Hans-Josef Buysch, Dorothea Garbe, Wilfried Paulus | title = Phenol Derivatives | series = Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry | publisher=Wiley-VCH | location = Weinheim | year = 2002 | doi = 10.1002/14356007.a19_313}}</ref>

==用途==
{{further|聚碳酸酯}}
双酚A的基本用途是生产各种塑料，这样的商品早在1957年就已经广泛出现在商业领域<ref name="infosheet">{{Cite web | title=Bisphenol A Information Sheet | date=October 2002 | publisher=Bisphenol A Global Industry Group | url=http://www.bisphenol-a.org/pdf/DiscoveryandUseOctober2002.pdf | accessdate=2010-12-07 }}</ref>。制造业每年至少要使用80亿磅的双酚A<ref name="USNews3">{{Cite news|url=http://health.usnews.com/health-news/family-health/heart/articles/2009/06/10/studies-report-more-harmful-effects-from-bpa.html|title=Studies Report More Harmful Effects From BPA|date=2009-06-10|work=[[U.S._News_&_World_Report|U.S. News & World Report]]|accessdate=2010-10-28}}</ref>。它是生产[[环氧树脂|环氧树脂]]的关键[[单体|单体]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.californiaprogressreport.com/2009/07/committee_succe.html|title=Lawmakers to press for BPA regulation|last=Replogle|first=Jill|date=2009-07-17|publisher=California Progress Report|accessdate=2009-08-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090722111113/http://www.californiaprogressreport.com/2009/07/committee_succe.html|archivedate=2009-07-22}} </ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thestar.com/article/415296|title=Ridding life of bisphenol A a challenge|last=Ubelacker|first=Sheryl|date=2008-04-16|work=Toronto Star|accessdate=2009-08-02|archive-date=2012-03-19|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66HIQv2FW?url=http://www.thestar.com/article/415296|dead-url=no}}</ref>，更是[[聚碳酸酯|聚碳酸酯]]塑料最常用的原料<ref name=Fiege/><ref>{{Cite book|last=Kroschwitz|first=Jacqueline I.|title=Kirk-Othmer encyclopedia of chemical technology|edition=5|volume=5|pages=8|isbn=0471526959}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.alliancepoly.com/polycarbonate.asp|title=Polycarbonate (PC) Polymer Resin|publisher=Alliance Polymers, Inc|accessdate=2009-08-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090921084954/http://www.alliancepoly.com/polycarbonate.asp|archivedate=2009-09-21}}</ref>。生产聚碳酸酯的总反应可以写成：

:[[File:Polycarbonatsynthese.svg|500px]]

聚碳酸酯塑料是一种透明且不易碎的材料，常被用于生产各种水瓶（包括婴儿用的奶瓶）、运动装备、医疗器械、[[牙充填|牙充填]]的材料、[[密封|密封]]剂、[[眼镜|眼镜]]镜片、[[CD|CD]]与[[DVD|DVD]]和家用电器外壳<ref name="CERHR">{{Cite news | title = CERHR Expert Panel Report for Bisphenol A | url = http://cerhr.niehs.nih.gov/chemicals/bisphenol/BPAFinalEPVF112607.pdf | format = PDF | accessdate = 2008-04-18 | date = 2007-11-26 | author = National Toxicology Program, U.S. Department of Health and Human Services | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080218195117/http://cerhr.niehs.nih.gov/chemicals/bisphenol/BPAFinalEPVF112607.pdf | archivedate = 2008-02-18 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。双酚A也被常用于合成[[聚砜|聚砜]]和[[聚醚|聚醚]]、在[[塑化剂|塑化剂]]中作[[抗氧化剂|抗氧化剂]]、在[[PVC|PVC]]的生产中作[[阻聚剂|阻聚剂]]。其中环氧树脂几乎被用于所有食品与罐装饮料包装的内层涂料<ref name="C&ENews">{{Cite journal|last=Erickson|first=Britt E.|date=2008-06-02|title=Bisphenol A under scrutiny|journal=Chemical and Engineering News|publisher=American Chemical Society|volume=86|issue=22|pages=36–39|url=http://pubs.acs.org/isubscribe/journals/cen/86/i22/html/8622gov1.html|access-date=2011-07-07|archive-date=2019-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190614072150/https://pubsapp.acs.org/isubscribe/journals/cen/86/i22/html/8622gov1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，处于对人体健康的考虑，在[[日本|日本]]，环氧树脂几乎完全被[[聚对苯二甲酸乙二酯|PET]]替代<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.foodnavigator.com/Financial-Industry/Consumers-fear-the-packaging-a-BPA-alternative-is-needed-now|title=Consumers fear the packaging - a BPA alternative is needed now|last=Byrne|first=Jane|date=2008-09-22|accessdate=2010-01-05|archive-date=2012-03-19|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66HIS4QXh?url=http://www.foodnavigator.com/Financial-Industry/Consumers-fear-the-packaging-a-BPA-alternative-is-needed-now|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。双酚A也是合成[[阻燃剂|阻燃剂]][[四溴双酚A|四溴双酚A]]的前体。以前它也曾被用于[[杀菌|杀菌]]<ref>[http://pesticideinfo.org/Detail_Chemical.jsp?Rec_Id=PC33756 Pesticideinfo.org: Bisphenol A]</ref>。生产[[无碳复写纸|无碳复写纸]]和[[感热纸|感热纸]]时，双酚A可以作为显色剂以实现复写或对热源产生反应<ref>{{Cite patent|US|6562755}}</ref>，前者被广泛应用在[[销售时点情报系统|销售时点情报系统]]的收银小票上<ref>{{Cite web|title=More evidence that BPA laces store receipts|url=http://www.sciencenews.org/view/generic/id/61490/title/Science_%2B_the_Public__More_evidence_that_BPA_laces_store_receipts|quote=Bill Van Den Brandt of Appleton Papers says that the receipts paper made by his company (which bills itself as the nation's leading producer of carbonless and thermal papers) is BPA-free.|date=2001-07-27|accessdate=2010-08-03|author=Raloff, Janet|publisher=Science News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100731084121/http://www.sciencenews.org/view/generic/id/61490/title/Science_%2B_the_Public__More_evidence_that_BPA_laces_store_receipts|archive-date=2010-07-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Concerned about BPA: Check your receipts|url=http://www.sciencenews.org/view/generic/id/48084/title/Science_%2B_the_Public__Concerned_about_BPA_Check_your_receipts|date=2009-10-07|accessdate=2010-08-03|author=Raloff, Janet|publisher=Science News}}</ref><ref name="ReferenceA">{{cite journal | last=Fukazawa | first=Hitoshi | last2=Hoshino | first2=Kentaro | last3=Shiozawa | first3=Tatsushi | last4=Matsushita | first4=Hidetsuru | last5=Terao | first5=Yoshiyasu | title=Identification and quantification of chlorinated bisphenol A in wastewater from wastepaper recycling plants | url=https://archive.org/details/sim_chemosphere_2001-08_44_5/page/973 | journal=Chemosphere | publisher=Elsevier BV | volume=44 | issue=5 | year=2001 | issn=0045-6535 | doi=10.1016/s0045-6535(00)00507-5 | pages=973–979}}</ref>。另外，双酚A也是输水管道的内层涂料<ref name="epa-action-plan">{{Cite web|url=http://www.epa.gov/oppt/existingchemicals/pubs/actionplans/bpa_action_plan.pdf|title=Bisphenol A Action Plan|date=2010-03-29|publisher=U.S. Environmental Protection Agency|accessdate=2010-04-12|archive-date=2011-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110204064057/http://www.epa.gov/oppt/existingchemicals/pubs/actionplans/bpa_action_plan.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由於酚甲烷是一種[[脂溶性|脂溶性]]的[[有機化合物|有機化合物]]，當高脂肪含量的食物用塑膠容器盛載，有可能會令塑膠內的酚甲烷釋出。[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]就曾因為市面上的椰漿含有較一般食物為高的酚甲烷而展在2005年展開調查，結果發現酚甲烷是來自椰漿包裝內層的塑料膜<ref name=pearl>{{cite episode en |url=http://programme.tvb.com/foodandtravel/whatreallyinourfood4/episode/3/ |title=Curry |series=食物大搜查 |serieslink=http://programme.tvb.com/foodandtravel/whatreallyinourfood4/ |episode=3 |station=[[明珠台|明珠台]] |city=[[香港|香港]] |date=2012-10-24 }}</ref>。透過減少塑料膜的酚甲烷，其後的調查發現椰漿的酚甲烷水平下降到安全水平以下<ref name=pearl />。

===塑料中的标识===
{{Main|塑胶分类标志}}
[[Image:Plastic-recyc-03.svg|thumb]]塑料在生产过程中可能接触过双酚A|left]]
[[Image:Plastic-recyc-07.svg|thumb]]塑料在生产过程中可能接触过双酚A|right]]
一般来讲，[[塑胶分类标志|塑胶分类标志]]为1、2、4、5、6的[[塑料|塑料]]不太可能在生产中与双酚A接触，而有一些（不是全部）[[塑胶分类标志|塑胶分类标志]]为3或7的塑料生产中可能接触到了双酚A。<ref>http://www.hhs.gov/safety/bpa/</ref> 

塑料制品上往往可以看到[[循环再造标志|循环再造标志]]和塑胶分类标志，标志中央印有包括1至7七个阿拉伯数字中的一个。其中的“7”代表所有的“其它塑料”，包括[[聚碳酸酯|聚碳酸酯]]（有时会在循环再造标志附近注明“PC”字样）和[[环氧树脂|环氧树脂]]，它们的生产原料都是双酚A。<ref name=Fiege/><!--When such plastics are exposed to hot liquids, bisphenol A leaks out 55 times faster than it does under normal conditions.{{Clarify|date=March 2009}}--><!-- Unit incomplete.  Nanogrammes per hour per how much of the plastic?  That much per mg would be a lot, per tonne not much. Also need to know what "hot" means, and what "normal conditions" means.--><ref name="sciam2008">{{Cite journal|author=Biello D | title=Plastic (not) fantastic: Food containers leach a potentially harmful chemical | journal=Scientific American | volume=2 | date=2008-02-19 | url=http://www.sciam.com/article.cfm?id=plastic-not-fantastic-with-bisphenol-a | accessdate=2008-04-09}}</ref>

3号（[[PVC|PVC]]）和一些7号塑料同样可能含有双酚A，因为在生产软质PVC的过程中，双酚A会作为[[抗氧化剂|抗氧化剂]]被添加到[[塑化剂|塑化剂]]中。<ref name=Fiege/>

